paragraphs.text:
%pyspark

fb= sc.parallelize(range(0,250))

print("number of partitions is {}".format(fb.getNumPartitions()))
print("partitioner is {}".format(fb.partitioner))
print(fb.glom().collect())

%pyspark

fb= sc.parallelize(range(0,250),20)

print("Default parallelism: {}".format(sc.defaultParallelism))

print("number of partitions is {}".format(fb.getNumPartitions()))
print("partitioner is {}".format(fb.partitioner))
print(fb.glom().collect())

%pyspark

#Custom Partitioner 

fb= sc.parallelize(range(0,25)).map(lambda l:(l,l+3)).partitionBy(10)
print("number of partitions is {}".format(fb.getNumPartitions()))
print("partitioner is {}".format(fb.partitioner))
print(fb.glom().collect())
